# Welcome to AutoKitteh. This Tour of AutoKitteh is an introduction to the
# programing model and is divided into multiple parts.
# To access a specific part, use the "Examples" select at the top of the page.
#
# AutoKitteh has three distinct concepts:
# - Event Sources, which send events;
# - Plugins, which affect side effects on the world;
# - A program, that tells AutoKitteh  what to do when an event is received
#   from Event Sources, and use Plugins to affect your deeds on the
#   world.
#
# The LitterBox is where we can play and try out various programs and
# see how they behave to different pre-recorded events.
#
# The LitterBox has three parts:
# - The Program editor, where you write the program to try.
# - The Event editor, where you stage an event to be sent to the program.
# - The Console, where you see your program "print" output.
#
